Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有着由善意而生的恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由恶意而生的善意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修所引起的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟应该归于哪一类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,审判是世界的必然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.67,0:00:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用这非人力量的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会逐渐尝受到心灵的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坠入善意与恶意的狭缝中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.44,0:00:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人能从中站起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人毋庸置疑将获得成为帝王的资格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 16
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}被囚的娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲二式再调整后的娴熟训练按预定的进行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.45,0:02:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都和印度军区之间已经联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是等开发小组和拉克夏塔的到达了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,组织的再编成现在实施到了92%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,构成人员从下层开始分成1至14个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照ZERO的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚所有的仓库也已经有我们的协力人员潜入了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关东地区
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:03:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人员和战力已经分散到全部564个地点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现的我方据点有32处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其中11处为假象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被逮捕的人员为47名
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于阶层8以上的的情报已经被遮断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚也找不到这以上的情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于有京都的协力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般群众向军队和警察通报的情况也几乎已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚内的协力者名单
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  是那个ZERO所准备的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  还有就是藤堂和四圣剑还在寻找中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续进行工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我作为使者可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果态度过于谦逊就会被人看不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦就是这样的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你不一样可是很谦虚的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就按这种状态去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,护照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又要被交给别的人家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是枢木的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次要去本家那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续走  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.24,0:04:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事  这种奇怪的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是在垃圾场的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解人的身体状况就要看眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是妈妈告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好上课会留级的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不是和我差不多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里有工作的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团的活动开始变得活跃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是技术部的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  因为人手不够  哪边都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是偶尔也来我家吃顿饭怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉感到很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有预定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  今晚没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是可以吗  会不会打扰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道会长相亲的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的话为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你的话你会哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会笑给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别在这种时候做这种天真的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天真？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种就被称为天真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么吃饭的事我就告诉娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  还有上课
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  只是去通知她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的烦恼置之不理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnDFPHSGothic-W5\fe128\fs25\b1\alpha&H15&}咲{\r}世子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的课不是从第二节开始吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相亲的话一般应该在饭店或是餐厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我听说罗伊德伯爵是个非常有个性的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有个性  还真是一个不错的表现方式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会接受被剥夺爵位而失势的阿修佛德家的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.60,0:06:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爵位这种东西无所谓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请你自便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不做也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么保留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉  朱雀他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是叫我在这里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我啊  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你大意了啊  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为我已经死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在C.C.不在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass无效的人是个麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.15,0:07:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事先放一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不还你上次的礼我实在忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该是在我的500米以内吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要来找我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时间限制是5小时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这是我和你之间的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用警察做卒子的话就NG哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想像上次一样被枪射
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是布里塔尼亚的医学还真是厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多亏这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那时下的Geass命令不应该是开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而应该是杀我才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.81,0:08:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后关头太天真你妹妹才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进入绝境了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,落入险境了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入危机了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这事和娜娜莉没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为游戏来说  这性质也太恶劣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你让哥哥伤心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.03,0:08:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会原谅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  现在是午休时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉和鲁路修吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.02,0:08:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  所以会长说暂时配合他们的陌生人游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相亲怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个还是莎莉和鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别管他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一样的夫妇吵架罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？  可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌  这和我没有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是没有越过那条线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那条线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修是只有理论但实战很弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,经验不够丰富
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,经验
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟  为什么你总是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呦  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你和莎莉怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,送她个礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  上课呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下午不去的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  晚上的事等会儿再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还在玩赌博吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.26,0:09:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看你到处找都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时间限制给你延长一小时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看穿我现在很焦急吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他为了读到我的心理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是在我的500米以内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然  娜娜莉发生了什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.17,0:09:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.08,0:09:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭马上就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说吃饭  你出去买过东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  只是用现成的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去外面还是害怕会有布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想起什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是什么都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧  不用慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢地想起来就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知合不合你的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架娜娜莉的家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是因为布里塔尼亚的旧账
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.01,0:10:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  和我们的身份没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想欺负女孩子的小鬼罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被威胁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被调查起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的身份也许会被揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不能通知军方和警察
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们自己想办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真的和赌博什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.15,0:10:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么有什么头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有照片和他在附近监视我这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  似乎有水流的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:10:59.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,循环系统
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地底的设施吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真少有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是平常的你的话  应该马上就会发觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,数据被改掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有破坏加密系统了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是违反校规吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之后回来修好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我来破坏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜  已经打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太熟练了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管理的一部分是由学生会接手的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在为止你经常使用这个偷溜到外面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  偶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和你推测的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,监视摄像机和机枪联动着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.21,0:11:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种系统的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,时间延迟大约有0.05秒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说从这里出不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重新回到上面一次把系统…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.56,0:12:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  还有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我现在马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.04,0:12:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.56,0:12:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至于擅自跟来的枢木我就不计较了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个人一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会把炸弹拆掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧  安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和鲁路修合作没有做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感应炸弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让运动停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的缆线一直给它提供能源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果受到这以外的力量作用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹就会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  可能只要娜娜莉一移动也会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样考虑会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能知道爆炸波及规模吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,半径500米以上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来毛在Geass的有效范围以外
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是引我上钩的手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道解体的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,理论上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把连在引爆装置上的电线切断就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是那家伙的本职
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以应该能分辨出假线
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  还是要考虑别的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能够区别出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在晃动中想要切断那根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是普通人能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.89,0:13:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.52,0:13:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.81,0:13:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情报太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确慎重是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有时间限制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要情报的话你眼前就有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么说也是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.84,0:13:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能使用我这个情报吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卫生纸还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上课好累
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是到毕业为止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是违规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个笨蛋教师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是轻松的小鬼们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为这样我才讨厌学校这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来他又想设置什么花样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.77,0:14:32.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛的位置应该在监视娜娜莉摄像机的发信地点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会回到学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乱来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然已经让朱雀别行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我所剩下的手段就只有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎  偷腥的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,武器和作战一概没有  炸弹还是放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团和刚才的朋友也没有利用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:57.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有闲情陪你废话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你准备了吧  最后的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  让我们决出胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用你得意的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没有过像现在这样的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来到11区以后有太多预想以外的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是做办公室的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有点发胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你不觉得这个花园很像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽安娜皇妃的离宫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  说起来的确很像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这里是克洛维斯哥哥指示建造的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他意外地还挺喜欢那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明总是和那儿的鲁路修吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.94,0:15:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是把他当成劲敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方可是比他小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是哥哥留下的画里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有鲁路修他们的画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要早日平定这个地区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然就很对不起克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及鲁路修和娜娜莉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的兄弟三人生命逝去的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个天平既是炸弹的引爆装置也是解除装置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要放上的是从对手那儿取得的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个指针完全偏向我的一边就会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全偏向你的一边炸弹就会被解除
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.41,0:16:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,换句话说  如果你赢了你妹妹就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:28.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是糟糕的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为被C.C.抛弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挑衅是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的内心可是一目了然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是能让脑袋变空白的那类人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是有一个作为批评家的自己在看着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此外还有看着作为批评家自己的另一个自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胜利都不会动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要同时考虑7件事以迷惑我的作战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我的Geass注意在你一个人的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要知道什么才是真实是非常简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.59,0:17:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  最后的策略也没有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.11,0:17:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果看轻我的话 你妹妹的生命就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,计策已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使使用其它人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.55,0:17:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但只要娜娜莉还是人质
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快一点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧看吧  时间就快没有了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹就会不在了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  走那步就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  毛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.22,0:18:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不清啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救救娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.01,0:18:20.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于听到你心底的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  会以怎样的状态粉碎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我的意识集中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亚军准尉枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以扰乱治安的嫌疑拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把炸弹解体了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  配合晃动的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要切断哪根电线鲁路修告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的指示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听到惨叫声就突入的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛  这样就算将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修  难道你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.40,0:19:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我用Geass让自己忘记了我指示朱雀的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:20:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我心里的声音当成全部情报的你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了解读我的心理被效果范围束缚而留下了漏洞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这家伙失败了你想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是如果不相信朱雀就无法实施的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnDFPHSGothic-W5\fe128\fs25\b1\alpha&H15&}咲{\r}世子  已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:18.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:22.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnDFPHSGothic-W5\fe128\fs25\b1\alpha&H15&}咲{\r}世子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这样就赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.71,0:20:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,放手  你这个杀父凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在7年前杀了亲生父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.91,0:20:41.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止决定彻底抗争的父亲的话战争就会结束？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上只是个杀人凶手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  我是…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被揭穿真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托周围的大人们全都说谎的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说军部发表的枢木首相自杀的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是个弥天大谎  全都是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.23,0:21:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不那么做的话日本就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才来亡羊补牢的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个自己想死的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要救人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想获救的是你自己的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以自己想要找死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以总是把自己逼入死境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的善意只不过是自我满足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.15,0:21:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想要得到惩罚的撒娇男孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾是喜欢你的  毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:21:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先去等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在C的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.94,0:23:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个愚蠢的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没有问毛关于契约的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还有朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么在再会的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.86,0:24:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.54,0:24:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始那家伙就想传达这一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.66,0:24:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候要是我能好好和他面对面的话
